release.notes:
Additional Installation Steps: Before ACollab will function properly as an add-on module, the ATutor and ACollab config.inc.php files need to be modified by adding the following lines, adjusting the values accordingly. Include the trailing slash.
		
		Add to ACollab's conif,inc.php file:
		define('AT_PATH','http://www.mydomain.com/ATutor/');
		define('AT_PREFIX','AT_');
		
		Add to ATutor's config.inc.pgp
		define('AC_PATH','http://www.mydomain.com/ACollab/');
		define('AC_PREFIX','AC_');
